No. 126,

Orig.

Kansas v. Nebraska et al.

First Report of the Special Master received and ordered filed. Exceptions to the Report, with supporting briefs, may be filed by the parties within 45 days. Replies, if any, with supporting briefs may be filed within 80 days. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., ante, p. 1001.]
